All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Component, FilterWidget, Service, Widget
public class NopFilterWidget
extends BaseFilterWidget

The No-Operation Widget that can be used in the configuration (aranea-conf.xml) to disable a Aranea widget that is enabled by default.

For example, to disable the transaction filter, insert the following line to aranea-conf.xml:
<bean class="org.araneaframework.framework.core.NopFilterWidget" id="araneaTransactionFilter" singleton="false"/>
